WEBVTT

00:03.539 --> 00:06.607
I don't want to be married.
I don't have to be married,

00:06.618 --> 00:08.986
You are not going to leave Adrian.
I'm not gonna let you.

00:09.021 --> 00:10.822
I think maybe I should
do what you did

00:10.856 --> 00:12.924
and just tell Ben I'm
thinking about going away.

00:12.958 --> 00:13.991
What?

00:14.026 --> 00:16.603
To New York.
To cosmetology school.

00:16.637 --> 00:18.106
The best way for you to learn
something is to get a job.

00:18.141 --> 00:20.777
You agreed to put money
into my account every week.

00:20.811 --> 00:22.844
Yeah, that's when I thought
you were seeing America.

00:22.879 --> 00:24.956
Daniel, do you think our
relationship is gonna last?

00:24.991 --> 00:28.020
I think it's a little too early for
us to be making any plans together.

00:28.054 --> 00:29.656
I want to go to
cosmetology school.

00:29.690 --> 00:30.960
I'm totally for it.

00:30.994 --> 00:33.971
What if I would need to go
to New York to study?

00:34.006 --> 00:35.038
That'd be great.

00:35.072 --> 00:36.839
And you're thinking
if Grace dropped Grant,

00:36.874 --> 00:38.677
then she'll drop
this guy too.

00:38.711 --> 00:40.713
And then finally, at long
last, she'll be free

00:40.748 --> 00:41.881
and you'll be in
the house with her.

00:41.916 --> 00:43.787
But I don't want
to be with Grace.

00:43.821 --> 00:45.055
Maybe we just need
a bigger place.

00:45.089 --> 00:46.924
Maybe we just need to
move back to my house.

00:46.958 --> 00:48.861
The three of us?
No, John and me.

00:48.896 --> 00:51.900
So what's the story?
What's your way out that was her idea?

00:51.934 --> 00:55.003
She could possibly go to
cosmetology school in New York.

00:55.037 --> 00:57.773
No. This is a lie.
I'm not buying it.

00:57.807 --> 01:00.777
Is it too soon for me to
try to get pregnant again?

